  p Welcome to Natours, we're glad to have you! 🎉🙏
  p We're all a big family here, so please make sure to upload your user photo so we can get to know you a bit better!
  table.btn.btn-primary(
    role='presentation',
    border='0',
    cellpadding='0',
    cellspacing='0'
  )
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='left')
          table(
            role='presentation',
            border='0',
            cellpadding='0',
            cellspacing='0'
          )
            tbody
              tr
                td
                  a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Upload user photo
  p If you need any help with booking your next tour, please don't hesitate to contact me!
  p - Jonas Schmedtmann, CEO
